     <H3>Travel</H3>
     <p>Participants will arrive at the Augusto C. Sandino International Airport (MGA) in Managua, Nicaragua. The SC team leader will 
         await the group at the main exit door holding an SC sign and wearing an SC T-shirt. We require that participants send us their 
         proposed flight itinerary for validation before booking as well as a complete flight itinerary so that we may ensure a smooth trip
          for all.
    </p>
     <p>On the arrival day, participants will have free transportation from the airport to the hotel. On the departure day, 
         participants are responsible for the travel cost from the hotel to the airport if the time they leave does not match with 
         the hotel transportation schedule. The cost of the transport is $6 and can be divided amongst several people.
     </p>
     <br>
     <H3>Liability</H3>
     <p>To best ensure the student’s health and safety during this trip, we require information on all dietary restrictions, allergies, 
         and medical issues.
        </p>

